==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Quindecemvir
<hw>Quin`de*cem"vir</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>;
<plu><it>pl.</it> E. <plw>Quindecemvirs</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>, L.
<plw>Quindecemviri</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[L., from
<ets>quindecim</ets> fifteen + <ets>vir</ets> a man.]</ety> <fld>(Rom.
Antiq.)</fld> <def>One of a sacerdotal college of fifteen men whose
chief duty was to take care of the Sibylline books.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Quindecemvirate</ent>⟦br⟧
